---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: '2026 Tax Success Story: Real Business Tax Savings',
  slug: '2026-tax-success-story',
  excerpt: 'Real 2026 tax success story with equipment purchase. How 0% down payment financing helped a business save RM40,000 in taxes.',
  date: '2026-01-22',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 5,
  category: 'Tax Planning',
  image: '/images/blog/tax-planning.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['tax success story', 'tax savings', 'equipment financing', '0% down payment'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "BlogPosting",
      "headline": post.title,
      "description": post.excerpt,
      "datePublished": post.date,
      "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": post.author },
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "Ing Heng Credit & Leasing Sdn Bhd",
        "logo": {
          "@type": "ImageObject",
          "url": "https://inghengcredit.com/logo.png"
        }
      }
    }
  </script>

  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Tax Planning</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>The Business Challenge</h2>

      <p>Meet Ahmad, a construction business owner in Klang Valley. His business was growing. Profits were increasing. Tax bill was getting bigger.</p>

      <p>He needed a solution.</p>

      <h2>The Problem: High Taxable Income</h2>

      <p>December 2025. Ahmad reviewed his accounts:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Business revenue:</strong> RM2.5 million</li>
        <li><strong>Net profit:</strong> RM450,000</li>
        <li><strong>Estimated tax:</strong> RM108,000 at 24%</li>
      </ul>

      <p>"Tax bill was too high. Needed to reduce taxable income. Accountant said buy equipment."</p>

      <h2>The Equipment Solution</h2>

      <p>Ahmad needed an excavator. His old one was insufficient.</p>

      <p><strong>Equipment cost:</strong> RM180,000</p>

      <p><strong>Bank quote:</strong>
      <br>• Down payment: RM18,000-RM36,000 (10-20%)
      <br>• Approval time: 3-4 weeks
      <br>• Equipment age: Under 5 years only</p>

      <p><strong>Ing Heng offer:</strong>
      <br>• Down payment: RM0 (0%)
      <br>• Approval time: fasts
      <br>• Equipment age: Any age accepted</p>

      <h2>The Decision</h2>

      <p>"Bank wanted RM27,000 down payment. That's RM27,000 less for operations. Ing Heng offered 0% down. Approved in fasts. Could buy used excavator too. Choice was clear."</p>

      <p>Ahmad chose Ing Heng Credit.</p>

      <h2>The Purchase</h2>

      <p><strong>January 15, 2026:</strong></p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Applied for financing:</strong> RM180,000 excavator</li>
        <li><strong>Approved:</strong> January 17 (fasts)</li>
        <li><strong>Delivered:</strong> January 25</li>
        <li><strong>Deployed:</strong> February 1</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>The Tax Benefits</h2>

