      <ul>
        <li><strong>Initial allowance (40%):</strong> RM72,000</li>
        <li><strong>Interest deduction:</strong> RM10,800</li>
        <li><strong>Total Year 1 deduction:</strong> RM82,800</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Tax Savings:</strong></p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Previous taxable income:</strong> RM450,000</li>
        <li><strong>New taxable income:</strong> RM367,200</li>
        <li><strong>Tax saved:</strong> RM19,872</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cash Flow Impact</h2>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background: #D4A574; color: white;">
            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #B8956A;">Factor</th>
            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #B8956A;">Bank</th>
            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #B8956A;">Ing Heng Actual</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Upfront Payment</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">RM27,000</td>
            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #E8F5E9;">RM0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background: #F5F0E8;">
            <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Cash Preserved</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">RM0</td>
            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #E8F5E9;"><strong>RM27,000</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Tax Savings Year 1</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Same</td>
            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>RM19,872</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Business Growth Impact</h2>

      <p>"Excavator arrived January. Deployed February. Took on bigger projects. Revenue increased 40%. Hired 3 more workers. Business expanded."</p>

      <p><strong>2026 Results:</strong></p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Revenue:</strong> RM3.5 million (up 40%)</li>
        <li><strong>Projects completed:</strong> 15 (vs 10 in 2025)</li>
        <li><strong>Staff hired:</strong> 3 new workers</li>
        <li><strong>Profit:</strong> RM650,000 (up 44%)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Ongoing Tax Benefits</h2>

      <p><strong>Years 2-5 Additional Deductions:</strong></p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Annual allowance:</strong> ~RM54,000 over 4 years</li>
        <li><strong>Interest deduction:</strong> ~RM43,200 over 4 years</li>
        <li><strong>Total additional:</strong> ~RM97,200</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>5-Year Total Tax Savings:</strong> ~RM40,000+</p>

      <h2>Ahmad's Advice</h2>

      <p>"0% down payment saved my cash flow. Preserved RM27,000 for operations. Tax savings reduced bill by RM19,872 Year 1. Equipment grew business 40%. Best decision ever. Don't pay down payment. Use 0% down. Keep cash for growth."</p>

      <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>

      <ol>
        <li><strong>0% down payment preserves cash</strong> for operations</li>
        <li><strong>Fast approval</strong> means quick tax benefits</li>
        <li><strong>Double tax savings</strong> from capital allowance and interest</li>
        <li><strong>Equipment investment</strong> grows business revenue</li>
        <li><strong>Used equipment option</strong> lowers cost further</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Your Success Story Starts Here</h2>

      <p>Like Ahmad, you can save thousands in taxes. 0% down payment preserves your cash. 100% full loan maximizes deductions. NO age limit expands options.</p>

      <p>We approve in fasts. Start your 2026 tax success story today.</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Create Your Success Story</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Get 0% down payment equipment financing and save thousands in taxes like Ahmad.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Phone)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Get Equipment Financing" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h3 {
    color: #8B6F47;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  strong {
    color: #2D1810;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  li {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #374151;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #D4A574;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  ol {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  ol li {
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  ol li::before {
    content: none;
  }

  br {
    display: none;
  }
</style>
